Andrey Arshavin on Mesut Ozil: &quot;As a player of course I respect him. Mesut is a world class player. But for me personally, he slows down the game. He also does not shoot enough. He always looks to pass and that makes it simple for the defense.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Andrey Arshavin on Arteta: &quot;When I go back to that time for a short period he became a captain and shown capabilities to lead and manage people. He would also always discuss how we need to play, at half-time and after the game. This showed his vision on the game.&rdquo;

